title: Our Biggest Fears | Ear Biscuits Ep. 354
description:
What do tiny demon girls, snakes, and Twitter have in common? They’re all things that scare us! #SpookySzn is here, so no better time for Rhett and Link to discuss some of their biggest fears. Find out why medium-sized crowds freak Rhett out and learn about Link’s potential DJ names. One thing’s for sure - after this one, you’ll never look at school mascots the same again.
